This directory (MAKE_SYSTEM) contains the KIM API service routines and related
files.

The contents of the directory are as follows:

COMPILER_DEFAULTS/
     Directory containing the various standard compiler default setting values

LINKER_DEFAULTS/
     Directory containing the various standard linker default setting values

Makefile.Generic
     Makefile containing common definitions for the KIM API make system

Makefile.LoadDefaults
     Makefile for loading default values the KIM API make system

Makefile.Model
     Makefile containing the KIM API make system's definitions for Models

Makefile.ModelDriver
     Makefile containing the KIM API make system's definitions for Model
     Drivers

Makefile.ParameterizedModel
     Makefile containing the KIM API make system's definitions for
     Parameterized Models

Makefile.SanityCheck
     Makefile that verifies all necessary settings variables have been
     set by the user and that they have appropriate values

Makefile.Test
     Makefile containing the KIM API make system's definitions for Tests

README
     This file

model_based_on_driver.cpp
     C++ code for creating a Parameterized Model
